[http://www.actiontec.com/products/product.php?pid=93 Product page] The '''Actiontec''' P/N for this device is ''probably'' GE144000-01. 1x 10Mbit WAN (RTL8019AS), 4x 10/100 LAN (w/ '''Kendin''' Switch) The schematics refer to this device as '''RENO'''. See also the [[Actiontec R3010UW]] and [[Actiontec R3010UW(AP)]].. Per the manual, the default SSID is '''ACTIONTEC'''.
